windows (s tseklant "isfuyla" s tutlayt tagyizit) d yiwet n tseddaṛt n inagramen n wammud id fres [[Microsoft]] iy selkimen imṣudan PC. D win id yarnan deffir [[MS DOS]].
Seg segwasen 1990, d ttwafɣa n Windows 95, id yemmugred arbaḥ ameqṛan, dɣa imi amaẓrag ines yestenya amtawa d waṭas imasraken n-iselkimen iwakken ad sveddayen deg furas nsen ala Windows 95 naɣ muyaf asen gen tafagwit n tedrimt, ayagi yeǧǧat ad yawi amḍiq ameqṛan deg ugduz.

taseddaṛt n Windows degs aṭas ifurkawen:
*Afurk amenzu, d win umi neqqar afurk 16 ibitten, iɣum Windows si lqem 1 ar 3.11 (3.2 s [[Tacinwatt|tcinwatt]]), Ifɣed asegwas n 1985, tleḥḥu (t-ttedddu) kan deg selkimen imṣudan PC, uqqin 16 ibitten.
*Afurk wissin, umi qqaren afurk Windows NT (Windows NT 3.1, NT 4.O, arnu Windows 2000), ifɣed di 1993. D taneflit id yalsen (iɛawden) seg ulac, ittwaxdem iy selkimen n yemdanen d iqeddacen d iselkimen imyagwan PC. Di tazwara llan seqdacent tmettiwin. 
Di 2001 Windows XP yeffɣed, yuɣal ufurk agi sseqdacent yemdanen marra, ayen yeǧǧan Microdoft ad ssuffaɣ wa deffir wayeḍ Windows Vista d Windows 7.
*Afurk wis kraḍ, umi qqaren tikwal afurk Windows 9x, yefɣed asgwas n 1995, idder s-umsaday d ufurk NT. Afurk agi yevda d Windows 95, yarnad fellas Windows 98 d Windows Me. Yettwassen aṭas seg imdanen, yarna yusad iwakken ad yeṭṭef amḍiq n ufurk amenzu, yella d-afurk amezwaru s 32 ibitten.
*Afurk wis kuz, umi qqaren afurk Windows CE, yefɣed asegwas n 1996. Yusad akken ad yeddu deg inagrawen yettwabban d warrumen fssusen n ufus (tilifun (teleɣri) ufus). d netta id azadur n Windows Mobile d Pocket PC.

